  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The goal of the study is to provide a detailed description of treatments for CRPC (Castrate
      Resistant Prostate Cancer) patients with bone metastases and the resource utilization and
      costs associated with that diagnosis and subsequent treatments.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
